<dd><p>Convert coefficient matrix to sparse format.</p>
<p>Converts the <code class=3D"docutils literal notranslate"><span class=3D=
"pre">coef_</span></code> member to a scipy.sparse matrix, which for
L1-regularized models can be much more memory- and storage-efficient
